<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="poison-vt">poison <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɔɪzn/    美 /'pɔɪzn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使中毒；毒死；使受污染：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Large amounts of industrial waste poison the water after they enter water bodies.
大量的工业废物进入水域后，会对水造成污染。</p><footer>译林新必修③ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>poisoning /'pɔɪzənɪŋ/ n   </p></div>